<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.9">
<l>icaivit teṉṉai yuṉṟā ḷiṇaikī ḻiruttu mammāṉē</l>
<l>yecaivi lamarar talaivar talaivā vāti perumūrtti</l>
<l>ticaivil vīcuñ ceḻumā maṇikaḷ cērun tirukkuṭantai</l>
<l>yacaivi lulakam paravak kiṭantāy kāṇa vārāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lord who incited [me and] made me sit under your pair of feet,</l>
<l>leader of the leaders of the motionless immortals, primordial great form,</l>
<l>you who lies while the world revers [you] tirelessly in sacred Kuṭantai, where</l> 
<l>ample big gems come together that throw rainbows in [all] directions, come [for me] to see.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
